n鄔幸恩小姐（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019<br />\n何小姐 (27歲)） - 4/9/2019<br />\n陳彥霖小姐 （15歲） - 19/9/2019(全裸墮海)<br />\n曾穎欣小姐 （26歲） - 7/11/2019<br />\n周梓樂先生（22歲）- 8/11/2019(被墮樓)<br />\n少女 (17歲) - 17/11/2019(全裸墮樓)<br />\n李女士 (45歲) - 18/12/2019 (全裸伏屍)<br />\n李仁博先生(32歲) - 19/12/2019(腳纏啞鈴墮海)<br />\n翁家倫先生 (41歲）- 23/12/2019 (被吊頸）<br />\n<br />\n元朗恐襲 - 21/7/2019<br />\n荃灣恐襲- 05/08/2019<br />\n太子慘案 - 31/8/2019<br />\n北角恐襲 - 15/09/2019<br />\n荃灣實彈 - 1/10/2019<br />\n西灣河實彈 - 11/11/2019<br />\n圍攻中文大學 - 12/11/2019<br />\n油麻地人踩人 - 18/11/2019<br />\n圍攻理工大學 - 16/11/2019 29/11/2019<br />\n理大廚房佬再被捕- 24/12/2019<br />\n<br />\n無數香港人被爆頭射眼性侵強姦輪姦被跳樓被跳海被斬手斬腳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好懶唔好慣唔好原諒香港警察</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"僆儂場擴大到任何角落！"},{"pid":"47e42034f68aa11e97e3ab309c64c327bb60dd0b","tid":1800681,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"812c45ce237797ae85f457bb3dbf8cc42e722558","tid":1800681,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"公司廁所都得<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n一月一日 維園再聚<br />\n一九之仇 二零必報"},{"pid":"69c4d9b804d5ca9883464028702a8be0a76c2bb1","tid":1800681,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a03b1cef55aaf2a2ded0b356376cb19e2f75b231","tid":1800681,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2682d7623470859245ad8500e444a2745975db9","tid":1800681,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:22:46.000Z","msg":"準備移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:35:59.000Z","msg":"最